{"tid":87961,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【真‧勵志故事2.0】80後收租王 買完柏傲灣儲夠4層樓","createTime":"2017-01-20T08:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T08:59:10.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d155e664fd0eca6a55f8abc959e498af4197bed","tid":87961,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"【短片】【真‧勵志故事2.0】80後收租王 買完柏傲灣儲夠4層樓<br />\n<br />\n2017-01-20 15:52:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】柏傲灣買家鄭先生指，由於自己已手持3個物業，今次用沒有物業的爸爸，以他名義買入柏傲灣800餘呎3房單位，涉資1300萬，打算付兩成首期，遲下先轉返自己名。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/163522_a9a90f8430438aa82fe0a81e7160af19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F163522_a9a90f8430438aa82fe0a81e7160af19.jpg&h=024bc65b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭先生又指，自己本身住同區海濱花園，所以都是心儀同區，年僅34歲已持有三個物業，有兩個位於荃灣，問及為何年紀輕輕已可有三層樓（未計今日買的柏傲灣單位），他直言是自己開公司，但未有透露做甚麼行業。<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃嘉銘<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經地產資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=TYQ1%2BmMmZHVeVTrycif%2BNpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c93df8da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n上一則: 【新界成交‧不斷更新】藍天海岸一房戶530萬新高價沽 九年賺3球<br />\n<br />\n下一則: 【貨尾動向】觀月‧樺峯削優惠 變相加價5%"},{"pid":"58936f7f703c080562464fc3e4b2cade34908dbd","tid":87961,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"呢個有冇得屌佢父幹撚，「用老豆個名買」?"},{"pid":"168e9ecd579c49692e94e5ebbfa829a1d0bc690e","tid":87961,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個有冇得屌佢父幹撚，「用老豆個名買」?</blockquote><br />\n避稅姐？"},{"pid":"d3ea4b3214911661c06b9349d2714e26491f0c34","tid":87961,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個有冇得屌佢父幹撚，「用老豆